snippet.title: The Story of Jozic - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
🕹️ Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1896900/Rail_Route_The_Story_of_Jozic 📅 Get on June 21, 2022
🚉 A stand-alone prequel from the developers of Rail Route, The Story of Jozic thrusts players into the world of an apprentice train dispatcher in the bustling city of Prague, guided through the process of creating their first rail network by a mysterious mentor.
